<section class="relative py-20 bg-background-dark">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-gray-800"
    >
      <div
        class="bg-surface-dark/50 p-12 md:p-16 flex flex-col justify-center border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-gray-800"
      >
        <div class="mb-6 opacity-50">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl mb-4">money_off</span>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-400">Traditional Model</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-500">
          <p class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500/50"></span>
            High Upfront Costs (CapEx)
          </p>
          <p class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500/50"></span>
            Monthly Retainers (OpEx)
          </p>
          <p class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500/50"></span>
            Financial Risk on Creator
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="bg-gradient-to-br from-surface-dark to-primary/10 p-12 md:p-16 flex flex-col justify-center relative overflow-hidden group"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/5 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"
        >
        </div>

        <h2
          class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6 relative z-10"
        >
          Not OpEx. Not CapEx.
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-invert relative z-10">
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            NeoGen is <span class="text-white font-semibold"
              >not an operational expense</span
            > nor a capital expenditure from your pocket. It is a <span
              class="text-primary font-medium">liquidity infrastructure</span
            > that deploys capital at risk in exchange for a share in future upside.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-4">
            By indexing our revenue to your success, we create a structural
            alignment where value compounds through <span
              class="text-white font-semibold">market diversification</span
            >, not through fixed-fee extraction.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-4 text-primary font-medium">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">trending_up</span>
          <span>Growth Driven</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
